CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1962, pg. C3, reads: "Photos of Your Pittsburgh Story Rally..."
TitMainTitle: Women, including Hazel Garland on left, and men, including Bill Nunn Sr. second from right, posed in Soldiers and Sailors Memorial Hall, for Pittsburgh Courier newspaper's Appreciation Day rally
